iption><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 15:45:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/golf/li-haotong-four-way-lead-after-first-round-dubai-desert-classic-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>巴西卢拉将于周五会见中国外交部长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/brazils-lula-meet-chinese-foreign-minister-friday-2024-01-18/</link><description>巴西总统发言人周四表示，巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦将于周五下午在巴西东北部城市福塔雷萨会见来访的中国外交部长王毅。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 15:36:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/brazils-lula-meet-chinese-foreign-minister-friday-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>印度NMDC表示没有计划向中国出口铁矿石</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-nmdc-says-it-has-no-plans-export-iron-ore-china-2024-01-18/</link><description>印度最大的国有铁矿石生产商NMDC Ltd周四表示，没有计划向中国出售铁矿石，正在扩大产量以满足国内需求。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 15:26:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-nmdc-says-it-has-no-plans-export-iron-ore-china-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，沙特阿拉伯仍在考虑加入金砖国家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/saudi-arabia-considering-brics-membership-sources-2024-01-18/</link><description>两名直接了解此事的消息人士周四告诉路透社，沙特阿拉伯继去年被要求加入金砖国家集团后，仍在考虑邀请其成为金砖国家集团的成员。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 13:48:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/saudi-arabia-considering-brics-membership-sources-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>随着新的进口和种植批准，中国对转基因作物的接受势头增强</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-embrace-gmo-crops-gains-momentum-with-new-import-planting-approvals-2024-01-18/</link><description>中国周四批准进口和生产更多转基因大豆和玉米品种，同时扩大全国种植面积，作为改善粮食安全和减少进口的一部分。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 13:46:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-embrace-gmo-crops-gains-momentum-with-new-import-planting-approvals-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>早间买盘：市场休息一下</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-18/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 11:06:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国通过丝绸之路大型港口拓宽南美贸易高速公路</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-widens-south-america-trade-highway-with-silk-road-mega-port-2024-01-18/</link><description>一个中国大型港口正在太平洋沿岸崛起，有望增强与南美的贸易关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 11:06:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-widens-south-america-trade-highway-with-silk-road-mega-port-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>沉阳文件未讨论出售中国宝马合资公司股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/no-discussion-sale-stake-china-bmw-joint-venture-shenyang-document-2024-01-18/</link><description>路透社周四看到的一份文件显示，宝马在中国的合作伙伴没有计划出售其合资企业的股份，这与本周早些时候的媒体报道相矛盾。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 10:39:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/no-discussion-sale-stake-china-bmw-joint-venture-shenyang-document-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>LME首席执行官计划于2024年与上海期货交易所签订第一批合约</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lme-ceo-aims-have-first-contracts-with-shanghai-futures-exchange-2024-2024-01-18/</link><description>伦敦金属交易所（LME）首席执行官在世界经济论坛（WEF）年会间隙告诉路透社，伦敦金属交易所（LME）计划今年试点使用上海期货交易所（ShFE）价格的合约。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 09:48:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lme-ceo-aims-have-first-contracts-with-shanghai-futures-exchange-2024-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>独家：如果边境保持平静，印度可能放松对中国的投资限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-could-ease-china-investment-curbs-if-border-stays-calm-2024-01-18/</link><description>印度一名高级官员表示，如果两国边境保持和平，印度可能会放松对中国投资的严格审查，这是印度可能取消长达四年的限制的首个信号。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 08:12:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-could-ease-china-investment-curbs-if-border-stays-calm-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>奢侈品集团历峰集团在华销量激增，股价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/luxury-group-richemont-posts-4-sales-increase-during-q3-2024-01-18/</link><description>卡地亚(Cartier)母公司历峰集团(Richemont)最近一个季度在中国的销售额激增，周四表明高端奢侈品市场的韧性，并推动这家瑞士手表和珠宝制造商的股价大幅上涨。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 06:11:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/luxury-group-richemont-posts-4-sales-increase-during-q3-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>众议院委员会对美国海军印太后勤提出质疑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/house-committee-raises-doubts-about-us-navys-indo-pacific-logistics-2024-01-18/</link><description>美国国会中国问题委员会致函海军部长，对从夏威夷将燃料转移到印度-太平洋地区储存设施的计划表示怀疑，并警告称，美国军方可能对可能发生的冲突没有做好准备。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 06:05:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/house-committee-raises-doubts-about-us-navys-indo-pacific-logistics-2024-01-18/</guid></item></channel></rss>